 "html": "<p>As jy vandag gaan braai, maak dit hierdie varkrepies.  Maak genoeg , want jul gaan te veel eet.  Lek jou vingers en jou lippe af!<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/rib-0181.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2021\" alt=\"rib 018\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/rib-0181-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>BENODIG:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>8 varkrepies</li>\n<li>125 ml soyasous</li>\n<li>100 ml tamatiesous</li>\n<li>2,5 ml komyn</li>\n<li>10 ml chillieflakes ( as jy van sterk hou)</li>\n<li>90 ml heuning</li>\n<li>5 ml  knoffel fyn gekap</li>\n<li>5 ml  gemmer fyn gekap</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>meng die boonste bestandele saam</li>\n<li>gooi oor die vleis en laat dit marineer vir n uur<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/ribresep-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2025\" alt=\"ribresep 003\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/ribresep-003-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>braai oor stadige kole  &#8211; die donker op die vleis is die suiker wat karamaliseer en is heerlik<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/rib-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2013\" alt=\"rib 003\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/rib-003-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>Bedruip die repies deurentyd in die marinade<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/rib-011.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2023\" alt=\"rib 011\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/rib-011-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Nou sit jy terug en eet jouself trommeldik.  Skink n glasie koud en hou aan eet.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/rib-032.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2017\" alt=\"rib 032\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/rib-032-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
